Darcy YUILLE
v.
Laurence V. PARNOFF et al. Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided June 5, 2019

Laurence V. Parnoff, self-represented, in support of the petition.

The named defendant's petition for certification to appeal from the Appellate Court, 189 Conn. App. 124, 206 A.3d 766 (2019), is denied.
